name: IMOV
additional_notices:
The following token has a variable tax function on the smart contract to change tax rates post deployment.
Do your own research and be careful if you are trading this token.

description.en:
IMOV is an inclusive fitness app for people of all abilities that lets you earn cryptocurrency while you walk and get healthy, we aim to nudge millions toward a healthier lifestyle and connect them to Web 3.0.
IMOV Metaverse Mission: Motivating the world user community to exercise more and earn more passive income based on health data, That gives a reason for the users to walk more often and use less vehicles which will reduce the carbon foot print.
